text: KHDC (90.9 FM) is a radio station broadcasting a Spanish Variety format. Licensed to Chualar, California, United States, the station serves the Salinas Valley and Monterey areas. The station is currently owned by Radio Bilingue, Inc. ==See also== *List of community radio stations in the United States ==References== ==External links== HDC Category:Radio stations established in 1981 HDC Category:1970 establishments in California Category:Community radio stations in the United States
